                <li><p>We use persistent cookies and session cookies. A persistent cookie stays in your browser and will be read by Us when you return to our Sites or a partner site that uses our services. Session cookies only last for as long as the session (usually the current visit to a website or a browser session).</p></li>
                <li>
                  <p>We may use the following cookies:</p>
